    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>A shadow writhes beneath the egg's protective membrane.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be <span class=\"name name-fuel\">nightmarish</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">soul-consuming</span>.",
