    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命的受精卵<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">隨時會孵化！</span><br><br>卵膜下有黑影蠕動。<br><br>掃描顯示基因可能天生<span class=\"name name-fuel\">如夢魘般駭人</span>且<span class=\"name name-fuel\">噬魂</span>。"
